(max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">DNY59/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By <a href=\"https://think.ing.com/author/padhraic-garvey/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Padhraic Garvey, CFA</a>, <a href=\"https://think.ing.com/author/michiel-tukker/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Michiel Tukker</a>, <a href=\"https://think.ing.com/author/benjamin-schroeder/\" rel=\"noopener\">Benjamin Schroeder</a></em></p> <h2><span>The recalibrated market discount for the funds rate exposes the 10yr rate as still too low here</span></h2> <p>The 25bp cut from the FOMC was expected, but the big</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2173183083/image_2173183083.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745246-rates-spark-long-end-rates-look-too-low-post-fomc", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 12:33:00"}, {"id": "4745243", "title": "Ripple: RLUSD Stablecoin And Its Impact On XRP In The Crypto Bull Market", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1135927483/image_1135927483.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Gold ripple stacked on a bright background of business graphics close-up. Ripple crypto-currency. Anonymous. Virtual currency\" data-id=\"1135927483\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1135927483/image_1135927483.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1135927483/image_1135927483.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1135927483/image_1135927483.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1135927483/image_1135927483.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1135927483/image_1135927483.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1135927483/image_1135927483.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1135927483/image_1135927483.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1135927483/image_1135927483.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Larina Marina</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Ripple USD (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/XRP-USD\" title=\"Ripple USD\">XRP-USD</a>) has been all the rage since the crypto market got into a bull trajectory, following President Trump's election win and his pro-crypto stance during the campaign. One crypto company to potentially benefit from possible policy</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1135927483/image_1135927483.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745243-ripple-rlusd-stablecoin-impact-on-xrp-crypto-bull-market", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 12:14:42"}, {"id": "4745238", "title": "Apple: Insourcing Can Structurally Lift Gross Margins", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/825721894/image_825721894.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Girl is runing on the city stairs and listening the music\" data-id=\"825721894\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1040px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/825721894/image_825721894.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/upl