tock:</p> <p></p> <h2>Thesis</h2> <p>Recent developments have overall made me even more bullish on the stock, which is</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/825721894/image_825721894.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745238-apple-insourcing-can-structurally-lift-gross-margins", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 11:48:00"}, {"id": "4745244", "title": "U.S. Quality Dividend Growth: Rebalance Summary", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Little piggy banks on ascending stacks of coins\" data-id=\"1072593728\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5423px\" height=\"3261px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Matt Wagner, CFA</em></p> <p>The rebalance of the <a href=\"https://www.wisdomtree.com/investments/index/wtdgi\" rel=\"nofollow\">WisdomTree U.S. Quality Dividend Growth Index</a> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DGRW\" title=\"WisdomTree U.S. Dividend Growth ETF\">DGRW</a>) became effective at the market close on Wednesday, December 11. This post provides the main takeaways from the changes to the Index and</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745244-us-quality-dividend-growth-rebalance-summary", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 11:40:00"}, {"id": "4745241", "title": "Rebalance Review Of The S&P Global Clean Energy Index - H2 2024", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/163716641/image_163716641.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Environmental and Ambient Data\" data-id=\"163716641\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"987px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/163716641/image_163716641.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/163716641/image_163716641.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/163716641/image_163716641.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/163716641/image_163716641.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/163716641/image_163716641.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/163716641/image_163716641.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/163716641/image_163716641.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/163716641/image_163716641.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Maxiphoto/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Abbie Zhang</em></p> <p>Launched in 2007, the <a href=\"https://www.spglobal.com/spdji/en/indices/esg/sp-global-clean-energy-index/\" rel=\"noopener\">S&amp;P Global Clean Energy Index</a> has been a headline benchmark for measuring clean energy-related companies' performance over the past 16 years. In April 2021, we launched the S&amp;P Global Clean Energy Select</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/163716641/image_163716641.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745241-rebalance-review-of-sp-global-clean-energy-index-h2-2024", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 11:10:00"}, {"id": "4745239", "title": "Small Caps Surge: High-Quality Opportunities For 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1256967959/image_1256967959.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Small Cap write on sticky notes isolated on Office Desk. Stock market concept\" data-id=\"1256967959\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6000px\" height=\"4000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1256967959/image_1256967959.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1256967959/image_1256967959.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1256967959/image_1256967959.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1256967959/image_1256967959.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1256967959/image_1256967959.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1256967959/image_1256967959.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1256967959/image_1256967959.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1256967959/image_1256967959.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">syahrir maulana</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Brian Manby, CFA</em></p> <p>After a stellar November, the final quarter of 2024 appears decidedly risk-on for U.S. equities. Galvanized by Trump's presidential election victory and the accompanying pro-growth, deregulatory agenda that markets anticipate, the S&amp;P 500 is routinely notching all-time highs.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1256967959/image_1256967959.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745239-small-caps-surge-high-quality-opportunities-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 11:00:00"}, {"id": "4745234", "title": "Tecnoglass: Time To Bank Some Profits", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157522571/image_157522571.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Skyscraper\" data-id=\"157522571\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157522571/image_157522571.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157522571/image_157522571.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157522571/image_157522571.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/15